ata-source-post_excerpt" ><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #777777;text-align: left" >We had the pleasure to talk about "Doing Good - feeling good?" with some prominent guests at Cloudfest 2021. Here are some of the main takings:   1) Education is a privilege Imagine your life without the time you attended school. Imagine not having had the opportunity to learn to write, read and do mathematics. For most of us, it’s probably hard to picture that, and it fills us with gratitude and awareness of how privileged we grew up. That is one of the main reasons for corporate as well as private donors to do charity: they want to give&hellip;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_clearfix"></div></div><div class="vc_grid-item vc_clearfix vc_col-sm-6 vc_grid-item-zone-c-bottom vc_grid-term-58"><div class="vc_grid-item-mini vc_clearfix "><div class="vc_gitem-animated-block  vc_gitem-animate vc_gitem-animate-fadeIn"  data-vc-animation="fadeIn"><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-a vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto-4-3 vc_gitem-is-link" style="background-image: url('https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/2021_School_Classroom-4.jpeg') !important;"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/its-time-to-celebrate-in-namibia/" title="It&#8217;s Time to Celebrate in Namibia" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><img class="vc_gitem-zone-img" src="https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/2021_School_Classroom-4.jpeg" alt="It's Time to Celebrate in Namibia" loading="lazy"><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"></div></div><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-b vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc_gitem-is-link"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/its-time-to-celebrate-in-namibia/" title="It&#8217;s Time to Celebrate in Namibia" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"><div class="vc_gitem_row vc_row vc_gitem-row-position-middle"><div class="vc_col-sm-12 vc_gitem-col vc_gitem-col-align-"><div class