pment-for-children-in-niger/" title="Christmas Project: Computer Equipment for Children in Niger" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"><div class="vc_gitem_row vc_row vc_gitem-row-position-middle"><div class="vc_col-sm-12 vc_gitem-col vc_gitem-col-align-"><div class="vc_icon_element vc_icon_element-outer  vc_icon_element-align-centervc_icon_element-have-style"><div class="vc_icon_element-inner vc_icon_element-color-white vc_icon_element-have-style-inner vc_icon_element-size-xl  vc_icon_element-style-boxed vc_icon_element-background vc_icon_element-background-color-custom" style="background-color:#3fb8b0"><span class="vc_icon_element-icon icon-basic-eye" ></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-c vc_custom_1623336174924"><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"><div class="vc_gitem_row vc_row vc_gitem-row-position-top"><div class="vc_col-sm-12 vc_gitem-col vc_gitem-col-align-"><div class="vc_custom_heading newsdate vc_gitem-post-data vc_gitem-post-data-source-post_date" ><div style="text-align: left" >Dezember 7, 2020</div></div><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_gitem-post-data vc_gitem-post-data-source-post_title" ><h3 style="color: #000000;text-align: left" ><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/christmas-project-computer-equipment-for-children-in-niger/" class="vc_gitem-link" title="Christmas Project: Computer Equipment for Children in Niger">Christmas Project: Computer Equipment for Children in Niger</a></h3></div><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_gitem-post-data vc_gitem-post-data-source-post_excerpt" ><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #777777;text-align: left" >Being hearing impaired or deaf does not hinder children from education. The only thing that could hinder them to succeed their school career is not having a specialized access to education. Therefore, the Niamey School of the Deaf needs Technology, Software &amp; Applications, Additional Materials, Teacher Training, Shipping of Material