lebrate the amazing opportunities&hellip;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_clearfix"></div></div><div class="vc_grid-item vc_clearfix vc_col-sm-6 vc_grid-item-zone-c-bottom vc_grid-term-59"><div class="vc_grid-item-mini vc_clearfix "><div class="vc_gitem-animated-block  vc_gitem-animate vc_gitem-animate-fadeIn"  data-vc-animation="fadeIn"><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-a vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto-4-3 vc_gitem-is-link" style="background-image: url('https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/f453ba_b711cc8199634531acfcd6bb05a4d5b2mv2_d_2048_1365_s_2.webp') !important;"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/a-fantastic-year-comes-to-an-end-thanks-for-your-great-support/" title="A Fantastic Year Comes to an End &#8211; Thanks for Your Great Support!" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><img class="vc_gitem-zone-img" src="https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/f453ba_b711cc8199634531acfcd6bb05a4d5b2mv2_d_2048_1365_s_2.webp" alt="A Fantastic Year Comes to an End - Thanks for Your Great Support!" loading="lazy"><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"></div></div><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-b vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc_gitem-is-link"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/a-fantastic-year-comes-to-an-end-thanks-for-your-great-support/" title="A Fantastic Year Comes to an End &#8211; Thanks for Your Great Support!" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"><div class="vc_gitem_row vc_row vc_gitem-row-position-middle"><div class="vc_col-sm-12 vc_gitem-col vc_gitem-col-align-"><div class="vc_icon_element vc_icon_element-outer  vc_icon_element-align-centervc_icon_element-have-style"><div class="vc_icon_element-inner vc_icon_element-color-white vc_icon_element-have-style-inner vc_icon_element-size-xl  vc_icon_element-style-boxed vc_icon_element-background vc_icon_element-background-color-custom" style="background-color:#3fb8b0"><span class="vc_icon_elem