tly. Currently, each task is assigned to a group of workers: one group has started to complete the ceiling; the other is plastering the interior walls. The building containing sanitary facilities is complete and shines in a new coat of yellow paint. The official opening ceremony for the school is scheduled for September 17, and we look forward to inviting our partners&hellip;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_clearfix"></div></div><div class="vc_grid-item vc_clearfix vc_col-sm-6 vc_grid-item-zone-c-bottom vc_grid-term-58"><div class="vc_grid-item-mini vc_clearfix "><div class="vc_gitem-animated-block  vc_gitem-animate vc_gitem-animate-fadeIn"  data-vc-animation="fadeIn"><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-a vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto-4-3 vc_gitem-is-link" style="background-image: url('https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/TL_0422-1024x683-1.jpg') !important;"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/opening-ceremony-in-nuevo-chimbote-peru/" title="Opening ceremony in Nuevo Chimbote, Peru" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><img class="vc_gitem-zone-img" src="https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/TL_0422-1024x683-1.jpg" alt="Children laughing" loading="lazy"><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"></div></div><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-b vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc_gitem-is-link"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/opening-ceremony-in-nuevo-chimbote-peru/" title="Opening ceremony in Nuevo Chimbote, Peru" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"><div class="vc_gitem_row vc_row vc_gitem-row-position-middle"><div class="vc_col-sm-12 vc_gitem-col vc_gitem-col-align-"><div class="vc_icon_element vc_icon_element-outer  vc_icon_element-align-centervc_icon_element-have-style"><div class="vc_icon_element-inner vc_icon_element-color-white vc_icon_element-have-style-inner vc_icon_element-size-xl  vc_icon_element-style-boxed vc_icon_element-background 