gitem-link" title="Vámonos – Let&#8217;s get started in Guatemala!">Vámonos – Let&#8217;s get started in Guatemala!</a></h3></div><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_gitem-post-data vc_gitem-post-data-source-post_excerpt" ><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #777777;text-align: left" >Our project in Guatemala made some exciting progress in the construction of a new school facility for underprivileged children. With a festive ceremony, the first stone for the additional classrooms of the San Antonio School was laid. Various community members and committees gave passionate speeches and, as is tradition, a pastor blessed the new ground. Parents and teachers are thrilled to start building the foundation for a better education for all their children. The official opening is planned for July 2019 because the construction work can mainly happen during the school holidays.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_clearfix"></div></div><div class="vc_grid-item vc_clearfix vc_col-sm-6 vc_grid-item-zone-c-bottom vc_grid-term-58"><div class="vc_grid-item-mini vc_clearfix "><div class="vc_gitem-animated-block  vc_gitem-animate vc_gitem-animate-fadeIn"  data-vc-animation="fadeIn"><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-a vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto-4-3 vc_gitem-is-link" style="background-image: url('https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/f453ba_6bb3431e394a437d82b19d18ef56b9a4mv2.png') !important;"><a href="https://groundbreaker.org/new-sanitary-facilities-for-the-school-in-peru/" title="New sanitary facilities for the school in Peru" class="vc_gitem-link vc-zone-link" ></a><img class="vc_gitem-zone-img" src="https://groundbreaker.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/f453ba_6bb3431e394a437d82b19d18ef56b9a4mv2.png" alt="New sanitary facilities for the school in Peru" loading="lazy"><div class="vc_gitem-zone-mini"></div></div><div class="vc_gitem-zone vc_gitem-zone-b vc-gitem-zone-height-mode-auto vc_gitem-is-link"><a href="https://g