e two – the construction of the upper level for additional classrooms. The children are already excited about the grand opening for the new premises, scheduled for the end of June 2019.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_clearfix"></div></div></div><div data-lazy-loading-btn="true" style="display: none;"><a href=""></a></div></div>